DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$b = random(2,5,1);
$t = -1+$b;
$n = $b;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Factor the polynomial \(x^4+$t x^2-$n\). Your answer can be written as
\((x+A)(x+B)(x^2+C)\) with integers \( A\), \(B\), \(C \), and \(A<B\)
$BR where \(A\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = -1;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(B\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  1;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and \(C\) equals:
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans =  $b;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.
